{"tid":625595,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手的第一百五天","createTime":"2018-04-11T14:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:43:29.000Z","uid":7686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d76893aa3cd290bf0db12788111eb3ba4bc0adf","tid":625595,"uid":7686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"不知從何開始，我讓讀書佔據我生活中大部分時間，內心一直想著如何把每一分每一秒都填滿。這樣充實的生活也令我沒有半分餘力去想起你，我也漸漸以為我真的開始忘記你了。可惜每當我把手頭上的事情做完後，無盡的悲傷與思念便會再次充斥在身體每一分每一吋肌膚之上。原來這一切由始至終都沒有解決，有的只有我的逃避。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我可以點做？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b94b7b5b12503a5184fcf63da9c3669ebe6d75","tid":625595,"uid":155325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係錯啦我"},{"pid":"7f93328281bb9d4f24ca61a3b005a6933efdb6fb","tid":625595,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}